author: Zhi-Hua Zhou and Yuan Jiang
title: NeC4.5: Neural Ensemble Based C4.5
window: To explore this issue, further experiments are performed on data sets (australian, page, thyroid voting, wdbc, wpbc) where neither NeC4.5 with µ = 100% nor NeC4.5 with µ = 0% is significantly more accurate than C4.5. The results are depicted in Fig.s 1 and 2. Note
